{"tid":17563,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"腸胃焦慮真係好撚辛苦","createTime":"2016-12-02T01:15:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T13:15:57.000Z","uid":40842,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec5dbcb9b3309d049aca5e67385e3bd75451ffea","tid":17563,"uid":40842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:15:20.000Z","msg":"朝朝都要提早起身坐下廁所<br />\n出門口搭車又要聚精會神用意志力催眠自己唔好肚痛，一感受到有小小肚痛迹象就要不斷大力深呼吸<br />\n不知不覺已經頂左10年，但身邊無朋友無屋企人明呢種心理壓力<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f77ac9314db0f6cd60ccc17e95edf093090a7d","tid":17563,"uid":4274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:17:01.000Z","msg":"我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d305ba794a66c6f18c6d0190af0cd1ab29a0046e","tid":17563,"uid":40842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:19:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好羡慕果d朝早一起身就可以安然自若地出門口返工返學，沿途放鬆傾電話打機睇片都唔會唔舒服既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"166cffccae407ae5e6dd024ed912e8d21e6bd787","tid":17563,"uid":28483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:20:35.000Z","msg":"我係成日胃脹 好辛苦"},{"pid":"e1d57811b9bd1d66b25e4f92a4c612b9e0d823d9","tid":17563,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:28:24.000Z","msg":"我唔知算唔算<br />\n無去check過<br />\n<br />\n一緊張就會肚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋朝朝起身都會肚痛<br />\n7點起身要到9點幾先敢食野"},{"pid":"4f84d0a083ff67dbcc0eb6db810e8759bb97228a","tid":17563,"uid":3643,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:57:57.000Z","msg":"叫 促腸易激症 （之類啦）<br />\n有時考試測驗present 都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會急屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4792b8f4540f4