"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T04:59:11.000Z","msg":"一塞車真係仆街，好驚又黎料。去到陌生既地方第一時間係記低D廁所位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0171f6a4d85be563b82e7a23ec34d998a12071","tid":17563,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:00:34.000Z","msg":"係咪肥婆成日質你食太多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb26dc49a7d768e5aafad2cd14bdf021f3f344b","tid":17563,"uid":42687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:10:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一塞車真係仆街，好驚又黎料。去到陌生既地方第一時間係記低D廁所位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以去日本最開心，d廁所勁乾淨，有年新年跟隻佬返鄉下真係仆街，d野食都唔預佢乾淨但d廁所污髒到我最後不吃不喝咁滯，返黎瘦左幾磅。"},{"pid":"78102447499885c1f2ba5b41eed190c971349f6d","tid":17563,"uid":33936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:15:48.000Z","msg":"我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實睇醫生都冇用 壓力問題"},{"pid":"5c466ad091d832a5c3c4d92686aa4c70ecc0a1db","tid":17563,"uid":23271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:17:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">食野落多啲美極</span>"},{"pid":"8fd1508a099ec91b923ce5fd600df74f61552241","tid":17563,"uid":48655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:21:05.000Z","msg":"我以前都有 一畢業就無左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43595dc47d6c1725c11a2f1b4c40ddb9b8ecff0d","tid":17563,"uid":21413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:32:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: orange;\">食野落多啲美極</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你真係好幽趣風默<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fddceab986c9bcde52d8445b8c6929d85f5a9dd0","tid":17563,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:40:59.000Z","msg":"胃氣勁<img src=\"/assets/fa